Package: emend
Title: Cleaning Text Data with an AI Assistant
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Emi", family = "Tanaka", email =
        "dr.emi.tanaka@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cph"), comment =
        c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1455-259X")), person(given = "Jiajia",
        family = "Li", email = "lijia970324@gmail.com", role = c("aut",
        "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-7143-9336")))
Description: Provides functions to clean and standardize messy data,
        including textual categories and free-text addresses, using
        Large Language Models. The package corrects typos, expands
        abbreviations, and maps inconsistent entries to standardized
        values. Ideal for Bioinformatics, business, and general data
        cleaning tasks.
